reviewText:
CAN'T STOP WATCHING THIS. LOVE THE GIRLS STYLE, ENERGY AND SOUND. LIVE IN THE STATES AND CAN ONLY DREAM OF BEING AT ONE OF THEIR CONCERTS. WILL BUY EACH AND EVERY DVD OF THEM. DOING DATA ENTRY ALL DAY AT WORK IS SO ENJOYABLE NOW THAT I HAVE THE "GIRLS" PLAYING IN THE BACKGROUND ON MY COMPUTER. SUCH A GOOD MOOD ENHANCING SOUND AND HOPE TO OWN ALL THEIR ITEMS BY YEARS END.
IF YOU ENJOY CATCHY MUSIC AND HARMONIZING VOICES THAT MAKE YOU WANT TO SING ALONG ALL DAY.......THESE "GIRLS" ARE FOR YOU!!! JUST LOVE THEM!!!
